The following global NPM modules are required:
npm install -g nodemon
npm install -g vows

The following NPM modules are required:
(Install in a sibling directory to the ExpressMVC directory, ie issue the command from
the parent directory of the ExpressMVC directory)
npm install underscore underscore.string
npm install express
npm install express-namespace
npm install express-params
npm install connect-form
npm install generic-pool
npm install mysql
npm install xml2js